high_descs: Step left to the left sink.
Take the soap out of the bottom left cabinet.
Walk right to the right sink.
Wash the soap in the sink.
Place the soap in the bottom right cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed bar of soap in a cabinet.

high_descs: Open the left most cabinet and grab the soap.
Re-position to the middle of both sinks.
Rinse the soap in the right most sink.
Back up a little bit from the sinks.
Place the soap in the right most cabinet under the right sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the rinsed off soap in the right most cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left, move to face the sink on the left.
Open up the left cabinet under the sink, pick up the soap in there.
Bring the soap to the right sink.
Wash the soap in the right sink with water.
Bring the soap to the right counter under the right sink.
Put the counter in the right counter under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put cleaned soap in the counter under the right sink.
